post_content: BASICS THAT ARE FAR FROM BASIC. Classic comfort meets unbeatable style with this Hanes Original women's plus-size tee. Our signature tri-blend fabrics come together to create a lightweight t-shirt that feels great on the skin. The just-right classic fit with curved hem, ribbed collar, and center back seam lend to an ultra-flattering look you'll love. Plus, it's made from recycled polyester for that super-soft, worn-in feel. Pair it with a nice jacket and heels for a night out or your fave Hanes sweats and a scrunchie for weekend chores around the house. You can't go wrong with Hanes Originals. BE YOURSELF IN HANES ORIGINALS - A stylish collection of cool, modern essentials designed for comfort, made for every body. SUPER SOFT & COMFY FEEL - Our best cotton, polyester, and rayon come together to make this soft and comfy t-shirt for women. RELAXED & FLATTERING - This women's t-shirt features a just-right classic fit and has a curved hem for a flattering and feminine touch. MADE WITH RECYCLED MATERIALS - A portion of this women's t-shirt was made with recycled polyester. COLD WATER WASH - Hanes recommends machine washing women's tees in cold water to reduce energy consumption.

post_title: Hanes Originals Womens Cotton Plus Size T-Shirt
post_content: BASICS THAT ARE FAR FROM BASIC. You'll see and feel the difference in quality and fit the moment you put on this Hanes Originals women's plus-sized t-shirt. We call this style the tee with the Goldilocks fit, not too tight, not too loose. It's just an easy body-skimming silhouette that's always flattering, especially with its slightly longer, subtly curved back hem. You'll love the soft, U.S.-grown cotton of this crewneck tee, as well as its versatility for layering or soloing. Other style details that make this tee a customer favorite are the slightly lower, ribbed crewneck and the center back seam that enhances the shape. We think you just might want this classic cotton tee in every color. BE YOURSELF IN HANES ORIGINALS - A stylish collection of cool, modern essentials designed for comfort, made for every body. A JUST RIGHT FIT - A body-skimming shape that Goldilocks would love, not too tight, not too loose. SHAPED TO FLATTER - A slightly lower ribbed crewneck and a curved back hem add feminine touches. Made from cotton or a cotton-rich blend depending on the color, this classic women’s t-shirt features sturdy details like double-needle stitching and a ribbed crewneck collar. A comfy, classic fit that is not too tight and not too loose will have you reaching for this cotton classic on repeat. HANES ESSENTIALS - Outstanding quality and value you have come to expect from Hanes. MIDWEIGHT COTTON - Midweight cotton fabric (some shirts are a cotton-rich blend, depending on the color) makes this a shirt you can wear all year. CREWNECK - This women's t-shirt features a classic ribbed crewneck collar. STURDY STUFF - Expertly constructed with double-needle stitching for extra sturdiness at stress points. Playtex Secrets Womens Ultra Soft No Poke Dreamwire Underwire Bra
post_content: COMFY, NO-POKE UNDERWIRE SUPPORT. Welcome to a world of dreamy underwire comfort from the Playtex Secrets® collection. This bra features a no-poke, no-pinch cushioned underwire and our 4-way support system with higher sides for coverage, fuller cups for natural shaping, wider straps for all-day ease, and a smoother back for enhanced stability. And all this amazing support comes in a feminine, smooth lace style that looks great under clothes. You’ll love how the adjustable straps help relieve shoulder pressure and convert from straight to crisscross wear for fashion flexibility with different necklines and shoulder styles. With a flattering V-neckline and satin trim, this could be the comfortable, supportive underwire bra you’ve been looking for. And it's no secret. ULTRA COMFORTABLE UNDERWIRE - The encased underwire provides no-pinch, no-poke comfort. 4-WAY SUPPORT SYSTEM - TruSupport® support system offers a thoughtful design of smooth and comfortable support, from cups to side to back to straps. FULLER CUPS - Non-foam, full-coverage cups reduce bulges and spillage. COMFORT STRAPS - To help reduce pressure on your shoulders. LOVELY LACE - This Dreamwire® underwire bra is made of smooth lace for a no-show look under clothes. SMOOTHING - Smoothing sides and back for a sleek, smooth look. MODERN NECKLINE - A graceful V-neckline with satin trim creates an updated and flattering look. CONVERTIBLE STRAPS - Wear your underwire bra with straight or crisscross straps for fashion flexibility under all kinds of necklines and styles. COLD WASH - Playtex recommends hand washing this women's bra in cold water to reduce energy usage and save money.

Hanes Mens Essentials Cotton Long Sleeve Pocket Tee
post_content: ESSENTIAL QUALITY, ESSENTIAL STYLE. Hanes Essentials men's long-sleeve tee combines total comfort and classic styling for a fit you'll love. Made from midweight cotton fabric (Light Steel is a cotton/polyester blend), this long-sleeve t-shirt is ideal for year-round wear. A front patch pocket details the front, while double-needle stitching, and shoulder-to-shoulder taping provide a sturdy finish. Perfect for layering or wearing alone, this timeless design pairs perfectly with everything from jeans to shorts or your best Hanes joggers. With multiple color options available, you can't go wrong with Hanes Essentials. HANES ESSENTIALS - Outstanding quality and value you have come to expect from Hanes. MIDWEIGHT COTTON - Cotton midweight fabric makes this a shirt you can wear all year. (Light Steel is a cotton/polyester blend). DESIGN DETAILS - Highlighted with a front patch pocket. BUILT TO LAST - Double-needle stitching and shoulder-to-shoulder taping make this a wardrobe essential you can depend upon. LAYER IT - Wear it as a bottom layer or as your only layer for easy styling. SO MANY OPTIONS - Available in multiple colors for even more must-have choices. COLD WATER WASH - We recommend washing this men's long-sleeve tee in cold water to reduce energy consumption.

Hanes Womens Performance X-Temp Polo Shirt
post_content: A CLASSIC POLO THAT KEEPS YOU COOL. When it comes to a classic like a simple polo shirt, you still want a polo that performs, a knit polo that you can wear under a blazer as well as to the gym. So we've designed this classic cotton-blend polo with our X-Temp™ technology that's designed to adapt to your temperature for all-day comfort. All the essential polo details are here, from a classic polo collar to a 4-button placket to short sleeves and a straight, even hem. Even better, this women's polo is gently tapered through the waist for a little extra feminine style. You'll love the feel of the soft cotton-blend knit, and you'll love the freshness it delivers all day. CLASSIC POLO STYLING - From the collar to the placket to the hem. STAY COOL - X-Temp technology is designed to adapt to your temperature for all-day comfort. FEMININE SHAPING - A slightly tapered silhouette for a little extra style. NO ANNOYING TAG - Tagless or tearaway-tag styling means no itchy tag to annoy you. COLD WASH - Hanes recommends machine washing women's polo shirts in cold water to reduce energy usage.

post_content: EMBRACE COMFORT. If you're looking for a totally smooth look with comfortable support, you'll love this Hanes Invisible Embrace wireless pullover bralette. Designed with removable foam cups for flexible support and natural shaping, this wireless bra offers a ComfortFlex Fit® with 4-way stretch that moves effortlessly with you. Hanes X-Temp™ technology wicks away moisture to keep you cool and comfortable all day. The V front works under all kinds of fashion necklines, and the pullover styling means no hooks or hardware to worry about. Know what's even better? This seamless, wireless bralette disappears under clingy clothes for the smooth, sleek look you want. COMFORT AND SUPPORT - Removable foam cups for flexible and natural shaping. ADAPTS TO YOU - ComfortFlex Fit styling with 4-way stretch means the fabric moves effortlessly with you. TEMP TECHNOLOGY - Hanes X-Temp technology wicks away moisture from skin to keep you cool and comfortable all day. SLEEK AND SMOOTH - Seamless cups disappear under tees and other clingy clothes, making this the perfect T-shirt bra. PULLOVER EASE - No hardware, hooks, or wires, just soft, smooth fabric. NO TAG, NO ITCH - Tagless styling for itch-free comfort.

Highlighted with wide, non-adjustable comfort straps, this pullover bralette offers a smooth fit with no hardware to pinch or dig or distract from your day. SmartComfort stretch technology combined with a ComfortFlex Fit® enhances its custom, body-hugging silhouette. Finished with moisture-wicking technology, this pullover bralette will keep you cool and comfortable even during your most active days. PERFECT FIT - Hanes SmartComfort stretch technology hugs your body for a flattering, custom fit. MOISTURE WICKING - Cool Comfort moisture-wicking fabric keeps you cool and comfortable even during your most active days. COMFORT YOU EXPECT - Comfort Flex Fit bralette is shaped to fit you, making it easy to find the right size. WIDE STRAPS - Detailed with wide non-adjustable comfort straps so a smooth, soft feel. SMOOTH FINISH - A clean finish, this women’s bralette offers a dig-free design with no elastic against your skin. WIRELESS - This classic wire-free design offers support and all-day comfort. post_content: Playtex Secrets bras are underwire bras with modern styling designed to fit your curves. Seamed, unlined underwire cups give you full, shapely support.
